                    <span>Excellent content, humorous, true, compelling, convincing but also alerting and worrying. Mintzberg shows us how far our actions reach, in this case actions of business schools and thus that we are more responsible then we at first hand might think. The book confirmed and deepened my understanding of the role of education, understanding what people have to learn and how they should be supported in their process. It's a truthful and insightful book!</span>
                  
              
